name: Swiss A340-313 [HB-JMB] Taxi and Takeoff from Tokyo Narita ᴴᴰ
description:
Dedicated to all the Swiss spotters out there, and especially GVA Spotter and ZurichAirportSpotter! Here we have Swiss International Air Lines' daily service to Tokyo Narita taxiing and taking off on runway 16R, on a 12 hour journey to Zurich. At only 12 years old, and looking like it, this four-holer will hopefully stay in the skies for a long time.

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
